==English==
===Etymology===
''Pot'' in the sense of a small glass of beer, though the term applies for any alcoholic drink.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[two]] [[pot]] [[screamer]]}}
# {{AU}} {{colloquial}} A person who becomes [[intoxicated]] or rowdy after drinking just a relatively small amount of [[alcohol]].  

